---
layout: layouts/listing.njk
title: Glossary
navSection: glossary
description: Pali terms used across these pages, with brief explanations and closest English renderings.
permalink: /glossary/
---

<header class="page-header">
  <p class="page-header__eyebrow">Reference</p>
  <h1 class="page-header__title">Pali glossary</h1>
  <p class="page-header__subtitle">
    Terms that appear throughout these pages — the closest English renderings, and a short note on what each word is doing.
  </p>
</header>

<section
  class="saved-guide glossary-guide"
  id="glossary-guide"
  aria-labelledby="glossary-guide-title"
>
  <div class="saved-guide__top">
    <h2 class="saved-guide__title" id="glossary-guide-title">How Pali notes work</h2>
    <button
      type="button"
      class="saved-guide__hide"
      id="glossary-guide-hide"
      aria-controls="glossary-guide-panel"
    >
      Hide guide
    </button>
  </div>

  <div class="saved-guide__panel" id="glossary-guide-panel">
    <ol class="saved-guide__steps" id="glossary-guide-steps">
      <li>
        <button type="button" class="saved-guide__step" data-guide-step="1" aria-pressed="true">
          <span class="saved-guide__step-num">1</span>
          <span class="saved-guide__step-text">
            Spot a <strong>dotted</strong> Pali word in any article.
          </span>
        </button>
      </li>
      <li>
        <button type="button" class="saved-guide__step" data-guide-step="2" aria-pressed="false">
          <span class="saved-guide__step-num">2</span>
          <span class="saved-guide__step-text">
            <strong>Click</strong> it — the word lights up.
          </span>
        </button>
      </li>
      <li>
        <button type="button" class="saved-guide__step" data-guide-step="3" aria-pressed="false">
          <span class="saved-guide__step-num">3</span>
          <span class="saved-guide__step-text">
            A <strong>note</strong> opens in the margin with a short gloss.
          </span>
        </button>
      </li>
      <li>
        <button type="button" class="saved-guide__step" data-guide-step="4" aria-pressed="false">
          <span class="saved-guide__step-num">4</span>
          <span class="saved-guide__step-text">
            This page gathers <strong>every term</strong> in one place.
          </span>
        </button>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <div
      class="saved-guide__demo glossary-guide__demo"
      id="glossary-guide-demo"
      data-step="1"
      role="img"
      aria-label="Animated example of clicking a Pali word and reading its margin note"
    >
      <p class="saved-guide__demo-label">On an article</p>

      <div class="glossary-guide__demo-page">
        <div class="glossary-guide__demo-article">
          <p class="saved-guide__demo-prose glossary-guide__demo-prose">
            The first noble truth names
            <span class="glossary-guide__term">dukkha</span>
            — not a rare crisis, but the friction woven into conditioned life.
          </p>

          <div class="glossary-guide__demo-inline" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="glossary-guide__demo-note-pali">dukkha</span>
            <span class="glossary-guide__demo-note-en">suffering / unsatisfactoriness</span>
            <p class="glossary-guide__demo-note-text">
              More than plain pain — the unsatisfactoriness woven into change itself.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="glossary-guide__demo-note" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="glossary-guide__demo-note-close" aria-hidden="true">×</span>
          <span class="glossary-guide__demo-note-pali">dukkha</span>
          <span class="glossary-guide__demo-note-en">suffering / unsatisfactoriness</span>
          <p class="glossary-guide__demo-note-text">
            More than plain pain — the unsatisfactoriness woven into change itself.
          </p>
        </aside>

        <p class="glossary-guide__demo-list" aria-hidden="true">
          Full list below ↓
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="saved-guide__caption" id="glossary-guide-caption" aria-live="polite">
        Look for the warm, dotted underline
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<p class="saved-guide-reveal" id="glossary-guide-reveal" hidden>
  <button type="button" class="saved-guide-reveal__btn" id="glossary-guide-show">
    Show how-it-works guide
  </button>
</p>

<p class="section-intro">
  Clicking a highlighted Pali word in any article opens the same note in the margin.
  This page gathers those notes in one place. Nothing here is a substitute for meeting the words in context.
</p>

<dl class="glossary-list">
  {% for entry in pali %}
  <div class="glossary-list__item" id="{{ entry.term | slugify }}">
    <dt class="glossary-list__term">{{ entry.term }}</dt>
    <dd class="glossary-list__en">{{ entry.en }}</dd>
    <dd class="glossary-list__text">{{ entry.explanation }}</dd>
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <p class="section-intro">Glossary entries could not be loaded.</p>
  {% endfor %}
</dl>
